This paper is about a tool and inference system for reasoning about the security of cryptographic protocols, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses state space reduction techniques, which are related to formal methods and logic (cs.LO), programming languages (cs.PL), software engineering (cs.SE), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
